Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Ford bounces back in opinion polls
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03zjl6r
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 8 Aug 1976
President Ford bounces back in public opinion polls. Nominee Carter now not such a shoe-in. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less